{"type": "article", "id": 23041, "title": "玻璃模块灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-01T07:34:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 72, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115126B6JGn1gSjLzfN4Zx.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组灯看似像旧时的钨丝灯泡，但它十足是 LED 灯。在水泥灯头下连接了扁平的玻璃模块，上面用激光雕刻了灯丝线，顺着灯光恰好可以看到清晰的纹路，有种特别的工业感，适合家居或酒吧环境。设计者来自以色列，6 种不同的玻璃模块可相互替换，<a href=\"http://www.illuminite.me/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115124jI7v6n29Vz4o1U8P.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.16361679\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115124PYsHeABQkn4TZ18o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115125G1A2DzYBsuJwVClE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115125KqSwRnGIWmoC643x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115126VqznXKNUIMGchFH2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}